  "2141040": {
    "name": "Formula Retro Racing - World Tour",
    "steam_appid": 2141040,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "《Formula Retro Racing：World Tour》是复古赛车的现代更新版，融合了 90 年代风格街机赛车容易上手的简单性与逼真的物理效果、分割画面多人游戏和 60fps 性能。<br><br>在大热的复古赛车游戏前作的成功基础上，《Formula Retro Racing：World Tour》加入了新的赛道和赛车类型，以增加游戏的深度。你将在全球各大标志性的地点进行比赛，与其他车手竞争，并尝试刷新你的单圈时间纪录。你是否有能力称霸每条赛车线，拥抱每一个过弯顶点，越过方格旗驶向胜利？<br><br>《Formula Retro Racing：World Tour》有四种游戏模式。分别为：<br><br>●\t街机<br>●\t大奖赛<br>●\t淘汰赛<br>●\t自由练习<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新一代的街机赛车</h2>你对街机赛车的了解和喜爱尽在于此，包括倒数计时、拥挤的赛车场和史诗般的撞车事故。灵敏的操控引擎带来现代赛车的感受，并为赛道上的每一瞬间增添了真实感。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/d0faa5c4d433de3f6c1fb918d1586442.poster.avif?t=1680274827\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/d0faa5c4d433de3f6c1fb918d1586442.webm?t=1680274827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/d0faa5c4d433de3f6c1fb918d1586442.mp4?t=1680274827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >现代的低多边形视觉效果</h2>归功于低多边形视觉效果，90 年代赛车游戏的粉丝会在《Formula Retro Racing：World Tour》中体会到回家的感觉——更新为 4k 解析度和清晰的 60fps 性能速度。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/0919ac4ce54bbb2ff5cb51bffaf5d387.poster.avif?t=1680274827\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/0919ac4ce54bbb2ff5cb51bffaf5d387.webm?t=1680274827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/0919ac4ce54bbb2ff5cb51bffaf5d387.mp4?t=1680274827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >赛车类型</h2>驾驶多种令人兴奋的新赛车类型参加比赛，包括高性能赛车和可以漂移过弯的肌肉车。这两类赛车中的每一类都有五种变化形式；五种不同的单座风格方程式赛车（包括旅行车，拉力赛车和雪茄形）与五辆肌肉车，从 40 年代到 00 年代的复古车辆。每辆赛车的操控都独一无二，让每条赛道都有不同的感觉。要由你来为每辆赛车找到最佳赛车线和煞车点。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/a03dbff98a124a1eb050149e72353483.poster.avif?t=1680274827\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/a03dbff98a124a1eb050149e72353483.webm?t=1680274827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/a03dbff98a124a1eb050149e72353483.mp4?t=1680274827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >标志性地点</h2>在伦敦、巴黎和纽约等标志性地点进行赛车，飞驰经过世界各地的著名地标。<br><br><strong>完整赛道清单：</strong><br><br>●\t蒙特娄<br>●\t伦敦<br>●\t巴黎<br>●\t罗马<br>●\t纽约<br>●\t拉斯维加斯<br>●\t柏林<br>●\t东京<br>●\t香港<br>●\t圣地牙哥<br>●\t旧金山<br>●\t史诺多尼亚漂移<br>●\t比睿山漂移<br>●\t迈阿密漂移<br>●\t圣塔莫尼卡漂移<br>●\t圣保罗漂移<br>●\t印第安纳椭圆<br>●\t亚拉巴马椭圆<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/b98d271e42b640fe4729874f66f33afa.poster.avif?t=1680274827\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/b98d271e42b640fe4729874f66f33afa.webm?t=1680274827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/b98d271e42b640fe4729874f66f33afa.mp4?t=1680274827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可破坏的赛车</h2>逼真的碰撞物理效果会将车辆撕成碎片，让你看到太过超越赛车极限的后果。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/cecde5673742aa732b3be4cbe7bb8ffd.poster.avif?t=1680274827\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/cecde5673742aa732b3be4cbe7bb8ffd.webm?t=1680274827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/cecde5673742aa732b3be4cbe7bb8ffd.mp4?t=1680274827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >分割画面多人游戏和排行榜 </h2>让你的朋友聚集在沙发周围，在四人分割画面游戏中正面交锋。看看谁的线路最快，或者干脆试着把对方撞翻。在最快单圈和比赛时间排行榜上与其他在线玩家一较高下。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/e3ebdd65dbb9617b55befdde29e101e3.poster.avif?t=1680274827\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/e3ebdd65dbb9617b55befdde29e101e3.webm?t=1680274827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141040/extras/e3ebdd65dbb9617b55befdde29e101e3.mp4?t=1680274827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >身临其境的 VR 体验</h2>用激烈的虚拟实境模式，让自己置身于紧张刺激的环境！这种完整的驾驶体验极为逼真，当你在 World Tour 的赛道上驾驶方程式赛车穿过弯道和发夹弯时，你的身体一定向弯道倾斜。",
